<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reliable-adj">reliable <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'laɪəbl/    美 /rɪ'laɪəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-dependable">1.★ <strong>可信赖的；可靠的 (dependable)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a reliable product 
质量可靠的产品</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom is clever while Jack is honest and reliable. 
汤姆聪明，而杰克诚实可靠。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>John is very <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (rely) — if he promises to do something he’ll do it.  （2009 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. reliable  </p></div>